OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777017944
OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,FThe BBC has axed Football Focus, with
OL,7,Fthe corporation saying the show would
OL,8,Fbe taken off air at the end of the
OL,9,Fseason after more than 50 years.
OL,11,FThe Saturday lunchtime programme was
OL,12,Ffirst broadcast in 1974, but the
OL,13,Fcorporation said in a press release on
OL,14,FThursday that changing audiences meant
OL,15,Fit was no longer as popular as it once
OL,16,Fwas, with people engaging with
OL,17,Ffootball content in a different way.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
