OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777017944
OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,FThe BBC's head of sport, Alex Kay-
OL,7,FJelski, said the decision had been
OL,8,Fmade before last week's announcement
OL,9,Fthat it needed to make #500 million
OL,10,Fworth of savings over the next two
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"Football Focus has been a hugely
OL,14,Fimportant program in the history of
OL,15,FBBC Sport and has played a key role in
OL,16,Ftelling the stories of the game for
OL,17,Fgenerations of viewers," Kay-Jelski
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@XO]
