OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777017944
OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,FKay-Jelski added that regular Football
OL,7,FFocus presenter Alex Scott would
OL,8,F"remain at the heart" of the BBC's
OL,9,Fsport output, including its coverage
OL,10,Fof next year's Women's World Cup in
OL,11,FBrazil.
OL,13,FThe BBC said The Football Interview
OL,14,Fwould move into the Saturday 12.45pm
OL,15,Fslot from next season. This season,
OL,16,Fthe programme has featured interviews
OL,17,Fwith Bukayo Saka, Emma Hayes, Bernardo
OL,18,FSilva, Hugo Ekitike and Michael
OL,19,FCarrick.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]
