OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777017944
OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,FA BBC release gave further context
OL,7,Faround the decision to bring Football
OL,8,FFocus to an end.
OL,10,F"Fans are accessing discussion,
OL,11,Fhighlights, analysis and news through
OL,12,Fdigital platforms and on-demand
OL,13,Fviewing and as viewing habits continue
OL,14,Fto evolve, it is right that BBC Sport
OL,15,Fadapts how it brings football coverage
OL,16,Fto the widest audiences across
OL,17,Ftelevision, radio, online and to its
OL,18,Fextensive social platforms," it stated.
OL,26,@rD@AOUzD@\O]
