OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,FFormer England and Arsenal striker
OL,7,FScott felt proud to have been
OL,8,Fassociated with the show.
OL,10,FShe wrote on Instagram: "52 years of
OL,11,Fan iconic football show.
OL,13,F"It's a show that I'll forever be
OL,14,Fhonoured to be associated with and one
OL,15,Fthat has made me grow as a presenter
OL,16,Fin a way I'll always look back on with
OL,17,Fpride.
OL,26,@rD@YOUuD@AOU
