OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,F"Thank you to everyone who has been
OL,7,Fpart of the journey, from the bottom
OL,8,Fof my heart it means so much. Time to
OL,9,Fget excited for big summer of sport
OL,10,Fahead."
OL,12,FFormer Football Focus presenter Dan
OL,13,FWalker felt it was "disappointing"
OL,14,Fthere was no longer to be a space in
OL,15,Ffootball's "constantly changing"
OL,16,Flandscape for a show which has "meant
OL,17,Fso much to so many people for so many
OL,18,Fyears".
