OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWalker, who hosted the show for 12
OL,12,Fyears, wrote on X: "Really sad to hear
OL,13,Fabout the end of Football Focus. I
OL,14,Floved that show growing up.
OL,26,@tD@TOU
