PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777017944
OL,3,CBBC axes Football Focus after 52 years
OL,4,Con British screens
OL,6,F"I used to watch it every week with my
OL,7,Fdad and I remember how proud he was
OL,8,Fwhen I got the job. It was such a
OL,9,Fprivilege to sit in the chair for 12
OL,10,Fyears, working with an amazing team on
OL,11,Fand off air and forming so many
OL,12,Flasting friendships.
OL,14,F"Saturdays were always special. The
OL,15,Ffootball landscape is constantly
OL,16,Fchanging and it's disappointing that
OL,17,Fthere isn't space for a show that has
OL,18,Fmeant so much to so many people for so
OL,19,Fmany years."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU{D@LO]
